{"tid":2243902,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 娜璉自曝「私底下的模樣連同公司歌手都認不出」？網笑：「超尷尬XD」","createTime":"2020-10-15T05:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T18:14:01.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc41baa16e349fb6ce55507d8c01ce852810b40","tid":2243902,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/10/14/550_1548419_1602684536.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F10%2F14%2F550_1548419_1602684536.webp&h=84d31cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓人氣女團 TWICE 成員娜璉小公主般、惹人疼愛的外貌受到許多粉絲們的喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n但近視的娜璉其實平時私底下大多時候是不戴隱形眼鏡，而是帶著眼鏡的，沒想到這件事帶來了意外的插曲。<br />\n<br />\n最近娜璉透露自己戴眼鏡的話會被認不出來，會這麼說是與同屬 JYP 旗下的男子樂團 Day6 成員 Young K 有關。<br />\n<br />\n娜璉解釋：「不久前在公司電梯遇到 Young K 哥，他對我說了「安妞哈誰呦」（敬語）然後我就什麼話也沒說」<br />\n<br />\n「但是大概靜止了五秒鐘，Young K 哥像突然被打醒一樣再次對我說「安妞」（半語）<br />\n<br />\n原來是因為 Young K 一開始誤以為娜璉是工作人員。<br />\n<br />\n對此，娜璉也說「 Young K 最後有認出來讓他很感動」，讓粉絲聽見爆笑不已、紛紛表示：「凝結的空氣太尷尬了」、「 娜璉什麼話也沒說太搞笑了」、「戴眼鏡還是很漂亮！」等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0OP3J9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0OP3J9.jpg&h=fc115b96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ffda6578a649321eb7efbe94298482fa95878e0","tid":2243902,"uid":93096,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:44:58.000Z","msg":"很肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e844d553ca510e70f4307f3dfb67fa15674647b7","tid":2243902,"uid":33359,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:45:48.000Z","msg":"其實公開場合佢個樣都唔見得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1547de62cf4e0afc4979ade663a45fcee2eeceb8","tid":2243902,"uid":368098,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/prChtck.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=